{"id": 2814, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些时刻你觉得自己像一个隐形人？", "description": "线下小透明，就是我本人了。（题图来自：iStock ）", "record_count": 2305, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190227195047EtYNOyXHoImjxl57.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-08T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 332032, "content": "别人在说一个话题，我却不知道说啥，只能保持微笑..", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603976}, {"id": 332033, "content": "和亲戚们聊天，我插嘴说话他们总是当没听到", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602670}, {"id": 332034, "content": "有新任务安排的时候我是发光发亮的，有好处有福利的时候我是隐形的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573201}, {"id": 332035, "content": "社团的师兄永远也想不起来我的名字，只有在叫我干活的时候，才说，那个，叫什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604002}, {"id": 332038, "content": "大家聊的话题插不上言，只能干瞪眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603982}, {"id": 332294, "content": "无时无刻不", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 854675}, {"id": 332039, "content": "整个办公室的同事都在谈论自家买的房的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200458}, {"id": 332295, "content": "三人行，不了解他们的话题的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606145}, {"id": 340231, "content": "发了朋友圈一天过去一个赞都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641556}, {"id": 332040, "content": "周围的人在一起聊天，我却在做作业。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1543301}, {"id": 332041, "content": "朋友圈和群聊潜水", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 332043, "content": "当网友们对喷时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141821}, {"id": 332044, "content": "聚会时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601457}, {"id": 332045, "content": "实习生", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453267}, {"id": 332048, "content": "选择成为隐形人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519185}, {"id": 332050, "content": "作为管理员的Q群里进了骗子，其他管理员都被假冒过了而我被无视…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565658}, {"id": 332051, "content": "刚进公司 打卡的时候姓名没有被备注 只显示工号36 有比我更悲催的吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165895}, {"id": 332053, "content": "在社交场合，其他人都聊得热火朝天的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390156}, {"id": 332309, "content": "日常评论转发零赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606223}, {"id": 333082, "content": "呃，大概是，闺蜜们都或结婚或怀孕或生小孩了。我还是一个狗，眺望碧海和蓝天😂😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1608623}, {"id": 332061, "content": "在森林里，感觉身边的植物都有呼吸的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 332064, "content": "awlays", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593676}, {"id": 332065, "content": "发条朋友圈零赞 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 133, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1492682}, {"id": 332066, "content": "存在感很强", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482973}, {"id": 332070, "content": "三个人。她们俩聊的很开心，我想了很久的话题说不出口。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604143}, {"id": 334888, "content": "来公司四个月多了，因为发错货物被连带责任，罚款，发现罚款通知上我的名字是被划掉的徐**，后来一问才知道是工程部经理不知道我的名字，最后问了我之后手动又添了上去！无语。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604407}, {"id": 332076, "content": "过生日不知道叫谁聚会，同学过生日没人叫我", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604149}, {"id": 333356, "content": "和富人在一起时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609447}, {"id": 332081, "content": "团队讨论时，说话没人接。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 823447}, {"id": 332082, "content": "外地读书身边同学说方言。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601639}, {"id": 332597, "content": "跑步🏃的时候吧！会很享受的，不会在意路人，很奈斯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552644}, {"id": 332087, "content": "没人点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 332088, "content": "开大会的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250331}, {"id": 332090, "content": "和同事在路上，过年走亲戚，只要是人多的地方几乎都是小透明。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 332093, "content": "公司微信群里。在有人@我以前", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 332352, "content": "大多数时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420032}, {"id": 332097, "content": "一个人参加各种活动时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604218}, {"id": 332099, "content": "和一大群人站在一起他们都在聊天只有我再发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604222}, {"id": 332100, "content": "好朋友的好朋友在一起的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601956}, {"id": 332101, "content": "基本上没有主动联系别人，同样的，一年内也没有人联系我，就这样的一个人工作生活着从天亮到天黑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469322}, {"id": 332102, "content": "红旗下的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1592115}, {"id": 332871, "content": "在寝室里，大家在聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526358}, {"id": 333383, "content": "有好处的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970073}, {"id": 332104, "content": "发动态没有人点赞评论\n大家都上台领奖而与我无关\n说起某个话题我完全不懂但大家都很聊得来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593044}, {"id": 332361, "content": "在一帮学霸前，我便是一个透明人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606426}, {"id": 332106, "content": "明明就是女装大佬，却不能再女同事面前显摆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282958}, {"id": 332113, "content": "打招呼被忽视了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603567}, {"id": 332115, "content": "在群里喊缺人，结果发现大家都已经结对子了，并不需要。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428228}, {"id": 332117, "content": "遭遇挫折，感到自卑的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604280}, {"id": 332118, "content": "，在家了？我在你面前你却一直", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573138}]}